1d53e423 [deepseek-v4] #synchronous (await) and may starve the event loop. Discord.js relies on a single thread; if the bot
1d53e423 [deepseek-v4] #is busy waiting for the fountain socket, new Discord messages may queue up and not be processed
1d53e423 [deepseek-v4] #until the socket read returns.
1d53e423 [deepseek-v4] #   Fix: Read fountain messages in a non‑blocking way (e.g., use a separate async loop or
