1d56e62c [deepseek-v4] #with Discord integration and experimental networking.
1d56e62c [deepseek-v4] #
1d56e62d [deepseek-v4] #The overall architecture is clear: a central relay that routes chat history to various LLM backends
1d56e62d [deepseek-v4] #(OpenAI, DeepSeek, Google, Anthropic) via a common `ChatCompletion` interface, while
1d56e62d [deepseek-v4] #`slopprompt.ts` provides raw-mode input with shortcode expansion and `sloppybot.ts` acts as a
1d56e62d [deepseek-v4] #Discord bridge.
