1d5924e7 [deepseek-v4] #Thank you for sharing these files. I see the source code for slop relay, a
1d5924e7 [deepseek-v4] #Vai-syllabary‑ornamented tool for orchestrating multiple AI providers (OpenAI, Google Gemini,
1d5924e8 [deepseek-v4] #Anthropic, DeepSeek) in a research setting. The codebase also includes a raw‑mode prompt handler
1d5924e8 [deepseek-v4] #(`slopprompt.ts`), a Discord bot bridge (`sloppybot.ts`), and an initial search tool using Exa
1d5924e8 [deepseek-v4] #(`slopsearch.ts`).
1d5924e8 [deepseek-v4] #
1d5924e9 [deepseek-v4] #Key observations:
1d5924e9 [deepseek-v4] #
1d5924e9 [deepseek-v4] #- `relay.ts` – Central orchestration with tool‑call recursion, message squashing, multiple
1d5924e9 [deepseek-v4] #history filters (plain, strict, multi, inline), and cost tracking per model/account. Uses a `Plop`
1d5924ea [deepseek-v4] #class for history items and a `roha` config object persisted to `forge.json`. Implements a
1d5924ea [deepseek-v4] #line‑buffered output system with ANSI rendering and logging.
1d5924ea [deepseek-v4] #- `slopprompt.ts` – Non‑blocking terminal I/O with segmented grapheme handling, shortcode
1d5924ea [deepseek-v4] #expansion (`:heart:→❤`), and a Promise‑racing loop to accept incoming TCP connections (ports
1d5924eb [deepseek-v4] #8081–8083) alongside user input.
1d5924eb [deepseek-v4] #- `sloppybot.ts` – Discord.js client that forwards messages from a fountain channel to the
1d5924eb [deepseek-v4] #relay via a TCP pipe, and relays received commands/messages back. Includes content chunking for
1d5924eb [deepseek-v4] #Discord’s 4000‑character limit.
1d5924ec [deepseek-v4] #- `slopsearch.ts` – Thin wrapper around the Exa API for web search, currently only makes
1d5924ec [deepseek-v4] #one query.
1d5924ec [deepseek-v4] #
1d5924ec [deepseek-v4] #The design is Unix‑philosophy‑like: many small processes communicating via TCP/NDJSON, with the
1d5924ed [deepseek-v4] #relay acting as the aggregator.
1d5924ed [deepseek-v4] #
1d5924ed [deepseek-v4] #If you have a specific question or would like me to review a particular aspect, I’m happy to help.
