1dab3259 [deepseek-v4] #the total cycles per iteration would exceed 8, but the instruction count itself is fixed. The
1dab325a [deepseek-v4] #`[16]` delay after `jmp` is present, but the loop lacks explicit delay instructions to match the
1dab325a [deepseek-v4] #subcarrier period.
1dab325a [deepseek-v4] #
1dab325a [deepseek-v4] #Recommendations
1dab325b [deepseek-v4] #
