1dab3ba1 [deepseek-v4] #1. Vertical sync & FIFO usage
1dab3ba1 [deepseek-v4] #   `out x, 32` followed by a loop reading pulse widths from the OSR implies the FIFO is pre‑loaded
1dab3ba1 [deepseek-v4] #with a table. The `out isr, 32` after vertical sync stores the line counter and pixel counter? The
