1dab3ba2 [deepseek-v4] #2. Active video loop
1dab3ba3 [deepseek-v4] #   `mov y, isr` loads the pixel counter (863) then `out pindirs, 1 [8]` shifts one bit from the OSR
1dab3ba3 [deepseek-v4] #each iteration with a 8‑cycle delay. This yields 863 × 9 cycles = 7767, but the active period is
