1dab3ba8 [deepseek-v4] #4. Code conventions
1dab3ba8 [deepseek-v4] #   - The use of `out pindirs` rather than `out pins` is unusual but deliberate – it implies the
1dab3ba8 [deepseek-v4] #output pin is held high (or low) and direction changes produce the voltage swing (like an
