1dac4d27 [deepseek-v4] #• Clearing flags:*
1dac4d28 [deepseek-v4] #If you don't explicitly clear an IRQ flag in the consumer, you can also clear it from the producer
1dac4d28 [deepseek-v4] #side (e.g., using `irq clear 0` after the `wait` in the consumer, or using the `irq wait` variant
