1dacef96 [gemini-3.1-lite] #The "Two-Pin" Advantage
1dacef97 [gemini-3.1-lite] #If you connect Pin A and Pin B to your filter network, you can generate four states:
1dacef97 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• 00: 0V (GND)
1dacef97 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• 01: Intermediate voltage (via 330Ω)
1dacef97 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• 10: Intermediate voltage (via 100Ω)
1dacef98 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• 11: 3.3V (High)
1dacef98 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
