1daf8877 [gemini-3.1-lite] #In PAL, the color subcarrier is f_sc = 4.43361875\text MHz. The Red color-difference signal (V) is
1daf8877 [gemini-3.1-lite] #modulated onto the subcarrier. The PAL standard dictates that the V component must be
1daf8877 [gemini-3.1-lite] #inverted on every other line.
