1daf887a [gemini-3.1-lite] #You mentioned a "solid red" pulse train earlier.
1daf887a [gemini-3.1-lite] #• Is it actually Red? In PAL, "Red" is not just a subcarrier phase; it is the combination
1daf887a [gemini-3.1-lite] #of the Luminance (Y) and the Chroma (U and V) components.
1daf887b [gemini-3.1-lite] #• The Logic Gap: Your `chroma.pio` is currently outputting a fixed phase sequence. This
1daf887b [gemini-3.1-lite] #will produce a "saturated" color, but it might not be exactly the color "Red" unless the
