1dafb052 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• The Wrap Size: You set the wrap to 9 bits (2⁹ = 512 bytes).
1dafb052 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• The Result: Since 120 words = 480 bytes, the DMA will read words 0 through 119, and the
1dafb052 [gemini-3.1-lite] #moment it finishes word 119, it resets its own internal pointer to word 0.
1dafb052 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1dafb053 [gemini-3.1-lite] #2. The "Feed Once" Logic
1dafb053 [gemini-3.1-lite] #You only call `dmachannelstart(chromadmachan)` one time in your `main()`
1dafb053 [gemini-3.1-lite] #function.
