1dafd8e7 [gemini-3.1-lite] #2. How it works
1dafd8e8 [gemini-3.1-lite] #1.  Start: You manually start `chromadmachan`.
1dafd8e8 [gemini-3.1-lite] #2.  Move: It transfers 120 words.
1dafd8e8 [gemini-3.1-lite] #3.  Chain: Upon completion, it automatically triggers `triggerdmachan`.
