1dbb2c76 [gemini-3.1-pro] #You are spot on to suspect the color burst length. Let us break down the exact timing of your PIO
1dbb2c76 [gemini-3.1-pro] #state machines to calculate both the burst duration and its offset (the "breezeway") from the start
