1dbb2c7a [gemini-3.1-pro] #• `irq clear 4` (1 cycle)
1dbb2c7b [gemini-3.1-pro] #• `out x, 32` (1 cycle)
1dbb2c7b [gemini-3.1-pro] #• `jmp !x start [16]` (17 cycles — delay is applied even when the branch is not taken)
1dbb2c7b [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1dbb2c7b [gemini-3.1-pro] #This is a 20-cycle overhead (0.282 µs).
