1dbb2c7c [gemini-3.1-pro] #• Total Breezeway = 0.282 µs + 0.902 µs = 1.184 µs*.
1dbb2c7d [gemini-3.1-pro] #• PAL Standard:* 0.9 µs (± 0.1 µs). Your burst starts slightly late.
1dbb2c7d [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1dbb2c7d [gemini-3.1-pro] #• The Fix: If you remove the `[16]` delay from the `jmp` instruction in `chroma.pio`, you
