1dbd9415 [kimi-k2.6] #│  `pio_sm_set_consecutive_pindirs(..., 2, true)`  │  Sets the PIO direction for both pins to **output**. Since your `chroma.pio` never executes `set pindirs`, this must be done from C.  │
1dbd9415 [kimi-k2.6] #╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
1dbd9415 [kimi-k2.6] #
