1dbda53f [kimi-k2.6] #
1dbda53f [kimi-k2.6] #The fix: shrink the line buffer to 64 words
1dbda53f [kimi-k2.6] #
1dbda540 [kimi-k2.6] #`64 words × 902 ns = 57.7 µs`. That is a near-perfect fit for one PAL line.
