1dbe3298 [kimi-k2.6] #
1dbe3298 [kimi-k2.6] #
1dbe3299 [kimi-k2.6] #On the RP2350 each PIO has its own set of 8 IRQ flags. An `irq set` on PIO0 is invisible to a state
1dbe3299 [kimi-k2.6] #machine on PIO1, so the chroma SM sits at `start` forever and never outputs the burst or colour
1dbe3299 [kimi-k2.6] #subcarrier. The FIFO fills but the pins stay at `0`, which is why the picture is perfectly stable
