1dbe5e67 [gemini-3.1-lite] #3. The "No Guesswork" Solution
1dbe5e68 [gemini-3.1-lite] #To eliminate guesswork, do not rely on the `[16]` delay in the `jmp` instruction, as it is coupled
1dbe5e68 [gemini-3.1-lite] #to the instruction pipeline. Instead, use a NOP-slide or a precise `y` counter in
1dbe5e68 [gemini-3.1-lite] #`wst.pio`.
1dbe5e68 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1dbe5e69 [gemini-3.1-lite] #• Modify `wst.pio` to be deterministic:*
1dbe5e69 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1dbe5e69 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1dbe5e69 [gemini-3.1-lite] #.program wst
1dbe5e6a [gemini-3.1-lite] #start:
