1dc00fbb [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The headers complete the picture well. A few things worth noting:
1dc00fbb [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fbb [claude-sonnet-4-6] #• Memory footprint*
1dc00fbb [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The frame buffers are substantial. Progressive: `8239 × 4 = ~32KB`. Interlaced even + odd fields:
1dc00fbc [claude-sonnet-4-6] #`(8270 + 8243) × 4 = ~66KB` combined. The RP2350 has 520KB SRAM so there's headroom, but it's worth
1dc00fbc [claude-sonnet-4-6] #keeping track of as the project grows.
1dc00fbc [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fbc [claude-sonnet-4-6] #• Preamble size difference*
1dc00fbd [claude-sonnet-4-6] #Progressive uses `linePreamble=4` while interlaced uses `evenPreamble=35`. That jump reflects the
1dc00fbd [claude-sonnet-4-6] #more complex interlaced vsync sequence needing equalization and serration pulses correctly timed
1dc00fbd [claude-sonnet-4-6] #across the half-line boundary — that detail is easy to get wrong.
1dc00fbd [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fbe [claude-sonnet-4-6] #• PetASCII*
1dc00fbe [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The presence of `PetAscii()` and a font sized for C64 character rendering is a nice touch. Combined
1dc00fbe [claude-sonnet-4-6] #with the teletext support it suggests a fairly capable text display layer.
1dc00fbe [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fbf [claude-sonnet-4-6] #• `fs.h`*
1dc00fbf [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The LittleFS stub implies flash filesystem support is planned. Given the RP2350's XIP flash, that
1dc00fbf [claude-sonnet-4-6] #would be a natural fit for storing teletext page content or character sets without exhausting RAM.
1dc00fbf [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fc0 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #• `ps2_init` taking a `PIO`*
1dc00fc0 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The signature accepts any PIO instance, but `vidbit.cpp` passes `pio2` which only exists on RP2350.
1dc00fc0 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #Worth a compile-guard if the code ever needs to target RP2040 as a fallback.
1dc00fc0 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
1dc00fc1 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #The architecture is shaping up coherently. Is `monobit.cpp` or `pal576i.cpp` the next piece?
1dc00fc1 [claude-sonnet-4-6] #
