1ddf4270 [deepseek-v4] #- The other PIO block's `pindir` writes will simply be ignored (or cause undefined behavior if the
1ddf4270 [deepseek-v4] #pin is switched mid‑line).
1ddf4270 [deepseek-v4] #
1ddf4270 [deepseek-v4] #Therefore, you must run both state machines on the same PIO block (e.g., both on `pio0`) if
