1de5e2f5 [deepseek-v4] #Summary
1de5e2f5 [deepseek-v4] #
1de5e2f5 [deepseek-v4] #This is a technically rich, ambitious project that pushes the RP2350’s PIO and DMA capabilities.
1de5e2f6 [deepseek-v4] #The main practical concern is the single‑buffered frame update, which will cause visible artefacts.
1de5e2f6 [deepseek-v4] #Fixing that and providing the missing `nitrohost.h` would make it ready for real use.
1de5e2f6 [deepseek-v4] #
1de5e2f6 [deepseek-v4] #Great work – I’d be happy to see a follow‑up with double‑buffering and active audio/input demos.
1de5e2f7 [deepseek-v4] #
