1dfed7d2 [deepseek-v4] #Thank you for sharing these PIO programs. They form a coherent set for a video generation system on
1dfed7d2 [deepseek-v4] #a Raspberry Pi Pico 2 (RP2350), likely for generating PAL 576i composite video with chroma, plus
1dfed7d3 [deepseek-v4] #audio (I2S/SPDIF), PS/2, IR, and teletext.
1dfed7d3 [deepseek-v4] #
1dfed7d3 [deepseek-v4] #Key observations:
