1dfed7d8 [deepseek-v4] #
1dfed7d8 [deepseek-v4] #The overall architecture is FIFO‑pipelined (pixelpump → onebit → threepin) with each stage
1dfed7d8 [deepseek-v4] #triggered by IRQs or pin feedback, achieving deterministic video timing without CPU intervention
1dfed7d8 [deepseek-v4] #after setup.
