1e0025e8 [gemini-3.1-pro] #In the RP2040/RP2350 PIO architecture, the FIFOs are strict first-in-first-out queues. They cannot
1e0025e8 [gemini-3.1-pro] #be indexed like an array (e.g., `[x]`), and the `mov` instruction cannot target the RX FIFO
