1e171846 [gemini-3.1-pro] #resets the Color DMA's read pointer back to the start and re-triggers it. It is entirely handled by
1e171847 [gemini-3.1-pro] #the DMA bus matrix, meaning zero CPU overhead.
1e171847 [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1e171847 [gemini-3.1-pro] #3. CPU Line Interrupt
