1e190176 [gemini-3.1-pro] #any issues. However, if you ever uncomment `CHROMA` to run both simultaneously on `pio1`, they will
1e190177 [gemini-3.1-pro] #fight over State Machine 1. You will likely want to change one of them to `0` (since `pio1` is
1e190177 [gemini-3.1-pro] #currently using 1, 2, and 3 for Pump, Audio, and Keyboard).
1e190177 [gemini-3.1-pro] #
