1e25ccca [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1e25cccb [gemini-3.1-pro] #
1e25cccb [gemini-3.1-pro] #4. Fix the State Machine ID and PIO Instance
1e25cccb [gemini-3.1-pro] #As discussed previously, `colorpump` must be on `pio0` to see `irq 5`, but in your original
1e25cccb [gemini-3.1-pro] #`vidbit.cpp` it was on `pio1` and shared an ID with Teletext. Make sure you have updated these
