1e2da12d [gpt-5.3-codex] #What stands out as new
1e2da12d [gpt-5.3-codex] #
1e2da12d [gpt-5.3-codex] #- Multi-stage color pipeline design is the big one:
1e2da12d [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- `colorpump.pio` emits 2-bit color index + one-of-four trigger pulse.
1e2da12e [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- `colorfifo.pio` machines (4x on `pio2`) act like indexed pulse-train lookup players.
1e2da12e [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- Per-pixel output is done as tri-state pindirs modulation for Y/Pb/Pr resistor DAC
1e2da12e [gpt-5.3-codex] #behavior.
