1e2da130 [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- video DMA
1e2da130 [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- optional interlace
1e2da130 [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- optional teletext packet injection
1e2da130 [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- optional chroma generator
1e2da131 [gpt-5.3-codex] #	- colorpump DMA feed
1e2da131 [gpt-5.3-codex] #- `vidpump.md` documents an alternate modular chain (`pixelpump -> onebit -> threepin`) which is
