1e3ca692 [deepseek-v4] #fountain). The roadmap section is empty; if that's new, maybe you plan to fill it in later.
1e3ca692 [deepseek-v4] #
1e3ca692 [deepseek-v4] #• forge.md* – The CLI reference is well-organized. Noteworthy: config flags 0-16, the
1e3ca693 [deepseek-v4] #`/share`/`/attach` behavior, `/push` for refreshing, and the forge prompt report format with
1e3ca693 [deepseek-v4] #cost/size/elapsed. The mention of "tool_call response prompt model for current time" under `/time`
