1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #
1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #4. The program does not handle sync or blanking
1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #If you use `grey.pio` alone, it will only output waveforms during active pixels (when triggered by
1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #a "stall" pin). During blanking and sync, you need the grey pin to be either high‑Z or driven low.
1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #Your calling state machine (e.g., `colorpump`) should set the index pins appropriately: for
1e3f1d31 [deepseek-v4] #blanking, set both index pins to a value that causes `rxfifo[y]` to yield a word with all zeros
