1e3f1d32 [deepseek-v4] #If the grey pin is part of a two‑pin luma DAC, you likely want a single PIO that drives both luma
1e3f1d32 [deepseek-v4] #and grey pins together. Currently you have separate PIO machines for colour channels; for luma it
1e3f1d33 [deepseek-v4] #might be simpler to have one machine that outputs 2‑bit pindirs and 2‑bit pins per pixel. For
