1e53d44a [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **JMP**            │  000                  │  Conditional jump to address         │
1e53d44a [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **WAIT**           │  001                  │  Stall until GPIO/IRQ/PIN condition  │
1e53d44a [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **IN**             │  010                  │  Shift bits into ISR                 │
1e53d44a [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **OUT**            │  011                  │  Shift bits out of OSR               │
1e53d44b [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **PUSH**           │  100 (IfF=0)          │  Write ISR to RX FIFO                │
1e53d44b [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **MOV** (RX)       │  100 (IfF=0, IdxI=1)  │  Write ISR to indexed RX FIFO        │
1e53d44b [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **PULL**           │  100 (IfE=1)          │  Read TX FIFO into OSR               │
1e53d44b [claude-haiku-4-5] #│  **MOV** (GET)      │  100 (IfE=1, IdxI=1)  │  Read indexed RX FIFO into OSR       │
