1e53d45d [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d45d [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d45d [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Destinations:*
1e53d45d [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `pins` – OUT-mapped GPIO pins
1e53d45e [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `x`, `y` – Scratch registers
1e53d45e [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `null` – Discard bits
1e53d45e [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `pindirs` – Output enable (direction) of OUT pins (RP2350 only)
