1e53d492 [claude-haiku-4-5] #11.5.4 Autopush and Autopull
1e53d493 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d493 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Autopull:* Refill OSR automatically when shift threshold reached.
1e53d493 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d493 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d494 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.out 8 left auto 8        ; Auto-pull after 8 bits shifted out
1e53d494 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d494 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.program autopull_demo
1e53d494 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.wrap_target
1e53d494 [claude-haiku-4-5] #    out pins, 1 [1]       ; Shift 1 bit, clock low
1e53d495 [claude-haiku-4-5] #    nop [1]               ; Delay, then...
1e53d495 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.wrap                     ; Hardware auto-pulls if needed
1e53d495 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d495 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d496 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Autopush:* Push ISR automatically when shift threshold reached.
1e53d496 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d496 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d496 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.in 8 right auto 8        ; Auto-push after 8 bits shifted in
1e53d497 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d497 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.program autopush_demo
1e53d497 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.wrap_target
1e53d497 [claude-haiku-4-5] #    in pins, 1 [1]        ; Shift 1 bit in
1e53d498 [claude-haiku-4-5] #    nop [1]
1e53d498 [claude-haiku-4-5] #.wrap                     ; Hardware auto-pushes if needed
1e53d498 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d498 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d499 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Shift counters:*
1e53d499 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- PULL / autopull clears OSR counter to 0
1e53d499 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- PUSH / autopush clears ISR counter to 0
1e53d499 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- MOV OSR/ISR clears respective counters
1e53d49a [claude-haiku-4-5] #- OUT ISR, n sets ISR counter to n
1e53d49a [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d49a [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Threshold:* 1-32 bits (0 encodes 32).
1e53d49a [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e53d49b [claude-haiku-4-5] #━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
