1e544dd1 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e544dd1 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Issues:*
1e544dd2 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- No alignment guarantees (should be `alignas(1024)` for DMA efficiency)
1e544dd2 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `progressiveFrame` is `extern` but only declared in monobit.cpp — linker dependency issue
1e544dd2 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- Frame data is cleared nowhere before first draw — uninitialized memory in video output
1e544dd2 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e544dd3 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• Recommendation:*
