1e7a1f90 [claude-haiku-4-5] #`SPDRP_PORTNAME` is a device registry property identifier. The full name is:
1e7a1f91 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e7a1f91 [claude-haiku-4-5] #• SPDRP_PORTNAME* - Device Property: Port Name
1e7a1f91 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e7a1f91 [claude-haiku-4-5] #It's defined in `setupapi.h` and retrieves the COM port designation (e.g., "COM3", "COM15") from
1e7a1f92 [claude-haiku-4-5] #the device's registry properties.
1e7a1f92 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e7a1f92 [claude-haiku-4-5] #Other common SPDRP_* constants include:
1e7a1f92 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `SPDRP_FRIENDLYNAME` - Human-readable device name
1e7a1f93 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `SPDRP_DESCRIPTION` - Device description
1e7a1f93 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `SPDRP_HARDWAREID` - Hardware ID string
1e7a1f93 [claude-haiku-4-5] #- `SPDRP_CLASS` - Device class
1e7a1f93 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
1e7a1f94 [claude-haiku-4-5] #These are part of the SetupAPI property identifiers for querying device registry data via
1e7a1f94 [claude-haiku-4-5] #`SetupDiGetDeviceRegistryProperty()`.
1e7a1f94 [claude-haiku-4-5] #
