1e97ee3a [gemini-3.1-lite] #The provided source code represents a sophisticated implementation of a software-defined video
1e97ee3a [gemini-3.1-lite] #signal generator for the RP2350 microcontroller. Utilizing the PIO (Programmable Input/Output)
1e97ee3b [gemini-3.1-lite] #blocks, the project achieves cycle-accurate timing for PAL 576i signal generation, including color
1e97ee3b [gemini-3.1-lite] #burst (chroma) and teletext (WST) insertion.
