1eab6cc4 [gemini-3.1-lite] #Why `piogpioinit` is required
1eab6cc4 [gemini-3.1-lite] #The RP2040 GPIO pins are highly multiplexed. By default, they are often set to SIO (Software
1eab6cc4 [gemini-3.1-lite] #Input/Output, controlled by the CPU). To use a pin with a PIO state machine, you must:
