1eab6cc5 [gemini-3.1-lite] #peripheral.
1eab6cc5 [gemini-3.1-lite] #2.  Set the direction (optional but recommended): While `jmp` is an input-only operation,
1eab6cc5 [gemini-3.1-lite] #it is good practice to ensure the pin is in the correct state.
1eab6cc6 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1eab6cc6 [gemini-3.1-lite] #Implementation Example
1eab6cc6 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1eab6cc6 [gemini-3.1-lite] #Here is how you should structure your initialization code:
