1ed28316 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1ed28316 [gemini-3.1-lite] #1. Enabling the State Machine and DMA
1ed28316 [gemini-3.1-lite] #The `piosminit` function sets the configuration, but it does not start the state machine.
1ed28316 [gemini-3.1-lite] #You must enable both the state machine and the DMA channel to begin the data flow. You should add
1ed28317 [gemini-3.1-lite] #these lines at the end of your `spdif_init` function (or call them immediately after):
1ed28317 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1ed28317 [gemini-3.1-lite] #
1ed28317 [gemini-3.1-lite] #// Inside spdif_init, after pio_sm_init:
