1f2874d8 [kimi-k2.6] #• How it works*
1f2874d8 [kimi-k2.6] #
1f2874d8 [kimi-k2.6] #• Rgnd (1 MΩ) again gives the guitar its DC reference.
1f2874d9 [kimi-k2.6] #• Rs, R1, R2 (all 1 MΩ) form an attenuator: the ADC node sees one-third of the guitar
1f2874d9 [kimi-k2.6] #voltage riding on a 1.65 V bias.
1f2874d9 [kimi-k2.6] #• Rlimit (10 kΩ) and the BAT54 clamp pair protect the Pico pin.
1f2874d9 [kimi-k2.6] #
