1f3e7de5 [kimi-k2.6] #Voltage level note
1f3e7de5 [kimi-k2.6] #If your microcontroller is a 3.3 V part, power the paddles from 3.3 V on pin 7 so the
1f3e7de5 [kimi-k2.6] #capacitor cannot charge above your pin rating. If you feed pin 7 with 5 V while using 3.3 V GPIOs,
